    <p>{`When creating a new class you will need to inherit from it corresponding creator, for the algorithm example: AlgorithmCreator. The creator class requires two template parameters. The first one is a unique name for the class, this name will be used to make some kind of dependency injection possible; and is used in the configurations files. The second parameter is the class itself.`}</p>
